{"tid":765704,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利華古遜堅夠薑　密謀簽卡利奧斯","createTime":"2018-08-03T03:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T04:24:40.000Z","uid":161311,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b1901575639b7a1c5fe8f494df6741a7fc95bbdd","tid":765704,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:57:34.000Z","msg":"利物浦神級膠龍卡利奧斯，上屆歐聯決賽兩度膠龍累紅軍失落錦標，今夏熱身賽連對低組別球隊都彈琵琶，認真令人失望。隨住巴西一號門將艾利臣比加加盟，卡利奧斯肯定失寵，正當大家以為卡利奧斯來季將長坐後備席嘅時候，外媒爆料德甲利華古遜有意斟仲呢名德國門將，而高普亦有意將佢賣走。 <br />\n<br />\n利華古遜今夏賣走賓特尼奴到阿仙奴，目前正搵緊代替人選，據報利華就係睇中卡利奧斯，希望填補門將空缺。查實卡利奧斯轉投利物浦前，效力緬恩斯時曾大獲好評，並入選《<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=YfP17A7Yj0qoJlgEaz2Ht10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=67397295\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>》德甲最佳十一人名單，如果佢來季重返德甲，離開英超球迷目光，最後可以重生都未定。"},{"pid":"da279b3a7fc5648af18bd91ce955253707757dae","tid":765704,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f84d0a183cb9f96673fed93256fd596680e0baa","tid":765704,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"我曼依排做乜貢落力<br />\n我地猁記手畜邊夠你玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7e4302929eb3638ed53dea2dedfca305a4c03d","tid":765704,"uid":171754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:08:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abcf11860d1757070e8588a83d4d51a677a794f7","tid":765704,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:11:51.000Z","msg":"可以買一送一比埋米勞列佢地"},{"pid":"75f2079b10f8b18dd3e1ee4993cd2c8c259b7373","tid":765704,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abcf11860d1757070e8588a83d4d51a677a794f7","tid":765704,"uid":581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T04:11: